title: MFSL MFCD  FILLS!  SILVER PACK #4 ALAC
description:
Here are 7 more of the MF CD Collection. I will continue to work on it but...

I have include a want list of the remaining ones. Also for your reading pleasure a doc of the facts and realities of digital music. As always please upload any that you have on that list.

This week or next I will be sending along the Audio Fidelity Collection So far it is only missing two. It is about 125 albums. Another high quality mastered collection.

Please seed everything so that others can get them as well. It means nothing to me as I already have them. However it is the right thing to do.

Enjoy!
